description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey.

Hometowns.


Philadelphia vs Bellevue, Nebraska.

City kid vs small town girl.

Water ices vs tater-tots.

Toyota Camry vs pick-up truck.

NY raves vs tail gate parties.

You get the picture.


"Wow. We had really different upbringings."
